Q
Qx = c
  \min_{x\in \mathbb{R}^d} \frac{1}{2}x^T Q x - c^Tx 
x=[x_1,\ldots, x_d]
Q=[q_{i,j}]_{i,j=1,\ldots,d}
 x^TQx=\sum_{j=1}^d\sum_{i=1}^dq_{i,j}x_ix_j=\sum_{j=1}^{d-1}\sum_{i=j+1}^d(q_{i,j}+q_{j,i})x_ix_j+\sum_{i=1}^nq_{i,i}x_i^2=x^TQ'x 
 Q'=[q'_{i,j}]_{i,j=1,\ldots, d}\quad q'_{i,j}=\begin{cases}q_{i,j}& \text{if }i = j\\ q_{i,j}+q_{j,i}&\text{if }i > j\\ 0&\text{if }i < j\end{cases} 
Q'
x^TQx=x^TQ'x
Q'
Q'x=c
  \min_{x\in \mathbb{R}^d} \frac{1}{2}x^T Q' x - c^Tx, 
Q'x=c
Qx=c
